## Demonwrath Targets

Shows an icon that pulses when `Demonwrath` ticks and displays
how many targets it hit.

![Screenshot](./screenshot.png?raw=true)

**Dev status**: Release

**Classes**: Warlock (Demonology)

**Requested by**: Arc
